724928f-a.text:
1765 York Avenue (formerly Avenue A), at N.W. corner of 92nd Street.
March 29, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.

724931f-a.text:
(1)
York Ave., north from Nast 92nd to 93rd Streets. This Ave. will extend northward along the East River, to form the new East River Drive. On the right, appears a portion of the Municipal Ferry to Astoria, L.I.
October 9, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, another view.
September 20, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
